high_descs: Move to the stove ahead of you
Pick up a pan from the stove
Move to the fridge to the left of you
chill the pan in the fridge for a moment
Move to the counter to the right of the fridge
Put the pan in the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan in a cabinet.

high_descs: Move over to the stove burners on the right-hand side.
Pick up the pan that is on the far right back burner.
Turn to your left and walk over to the fridge that is now on your right.
Place the pan inside the fridge to cool before pulling it back out.
Take the pan out of the fridge and move over to the lower cabinet to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the pan in the cabinet and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled pan into a cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the right side of the stove.
Pick the pan up from the stove.
Go to the left and face the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the pan back out.
Move to the right of the fridge in front of the lower cabinets.
Put the pan in the lower left cabinet and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan in a cabinet.
